  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2></strong><br>Crashy Laps is a game to enjoy driving and overtaking aggressively where collisions and foul play are common, with a maximum of 4 Players. 20 little and funny tracks are waiting for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/5ee50b486488ec5bcdca5c0573847b22.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/5ee50b486488ec5bcdca5c0573847b22.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/5ee50b486488ec5bcdca5c0573847b22.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In Single Player mode, you can also compete to reach the Best Time in the Leaderboard of each track.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/0f17fee4e1255c037226c24e49ecdbd7.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/0f17fee4e1255c037226c24e49ecdbd7.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/0f17fee4e1255c037226c24e49ecdbd7.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use one or more <strong>Gamepads </strong>🎮, or <strong>Keyboard </strong>⌨️: you can use Keyboard for playing a maximum of 2 players at the same time.<br></li><li>4 Settings for each part of day: Morning, Midday ☀, Evening 🌄 and Night 🌛.<br></li><li>4 Competitions: Time Trial, Quick Race, Grand Prix and Championship.<br></li><li>4 Areas with their own settings: road grip, environment, terrain types, etc.<br></li><li>4 Tracks for each Area: <strong>16 Tracks + 4 Track variants.</strong><br></li><li>3 AI 🤖 Difficulties: Novice, Professional and Expert.<br></li><li>2 selectable Camera Views: <strong>Isometric or Top-down</strong>. Zoom in or out to adjust screen for aspects ratio from 4:3 until 21:9.<br></li><li>2 selectable Engine Sounds: Combustion or Electric.<br></li><li><strong>Customization</strong>: customize the number and the car colours.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/2dabf4d10bb6234afd84701ca99a91ac.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=600 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/2dabf4d10bb6234afd84701ca99a91ac.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Competitions</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time Trial 🏎️: play in Single Player mode and try to reach your Best Time and the World Record for each track.<br></li><li>Quick Race, from 🏎️🏎️ to 🏎️🏎️🏎️🏎️: play a 4 laps race.<br></li><li>Grand Prix 🏎️🏎️🏎️🏎️: play a Grand Prix with a qualifying lap for each player and 4 laps race.<br></li><li>Championship 🏎️🏎️🏎️🏎️: play a Championship competing in the 4 Tracks of the selected Area and reach the Championship Cups by the selected difficulty.</li></ul><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zones</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Candy Lands</strong>: drive in a sweet world where the mud is chocolate, on simple roads great for beginners.<br></li><li><strong>Alpine Bridge</strong>: drive in an alpine area, always crossing bridges and tunnels.<br></li><li><strong>Silver Dunes</strong>: drive in a desert area, on rough and uneven roads.<br></li><li><strong>Frosty Way</strong>: drive in an icy area surrounded by snowy mountains, on slippery and twisty roads.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/d0fee46991af10682a960e1ef35baed2.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=150 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/d0fee46991af10682a960e1ef35baed2.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/d0fee46991af10682a960e1ef35baed2.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/68b8e376d04074dfaecac51ce8ed22b8.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=150 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/68b8e376d04074dfaecac51ce8ed22b8.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/68b8e376d04074dfaecac51ce8ed22b8.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/61b60b58c8c85d57d99866ad9427e487.poster.avif?t=1726465199\" width=150 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/61b60b58c8c85d57d99866ad9427e487.webm?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257410/extras/61b60b58c8c85d57d99866ad9427e487.mp4?t=1726465199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></vid